aces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n附近有個公園都幾好 (前身試過做巴士總站，又試過做golf場，好彩最後係公園咋，都叫冇咁壓迫)<br />\n<br />\n不過要注意隔離就係學校，如果望正都幾嘈下<br />\n同埋學校後面就係highway 都會有d車聲<br />\n<br />\n當然我估你應該都係買向海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以以上問題唔係問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屋苑入面就要等其他巴絲comment下<br />\n不過我覺得佢比嘉亨灣抵買 回報率應該高d<br />\n<br />\nbtw 三公子聽曬grade 8 d歌未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd4d2aef8f5a85140fcb317420e474e4fd00cb3c","tid":2166712,"uid":26436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fcc65ad413fc6c3c8bf573c9858ef3059fd39e0","tid":2166712,"uid":356725,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T16:56:42.000Z","msg":"我自己冇住過<br />\n不過對附近環境都知少少<br />\n<br />\n西灣河其實幾好住<br />\n一上highway去邊都好快 當然塞車另計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n附近小食店太安樓好多野食 雖然未必岩你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但另一邊蘇豪區都好正下 有酒吧之餘都有幾間日本小店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (唔知疫情有冇執到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n附近有個公園都幾好 (前身試過做巴士總站，又試過做golf場，好彩最後係公園咋，都叫冇咁壓迫)<br />\n<br />\n不過要注意隔離就係學校，如果望正都幾嘈下<br />\n同埋學校後面就係highway 都會有d車聲<br />\n<br />\n當然我估你應該都係買向海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以以上問題唔係問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屋苑入面就要等其他巴絲comment下<br />\n不過我覺得佢比嘉亨灣抵買 回報率應該高d<br />\n<br />\nbtw 三公子聽曬grade 8 d歌未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T16:59:00.000Z","msg":"未得閒住，呢排忙睇樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9c317e02f33d84f5088c3aa0c11eaa0ad8b8543","tid":2166712,"uid":125261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73bfc317eb919f3c7525564b